description: Startech offers a full aftermarket makeover for the Tesla Model 3 for around USD$17,000. This makeover includes a bodykit complete with a spoiler that is said to be inspired by Formula 1 cars, faux carbon fiber trim inside and out, custom-designed 20-inch rims and a 30 ~ 40mm lowering kit. Shmee150 has featured and driven it on his YouTube channel, you can watch the video [here](https://youtu.be/7WO9EWfNRWY).
creator: Keanny
